Sea World Puzzle – We promise you will love this match 3 game. It will help you to train your mind and relax. If you love sea animals – you will love this game!

INTRODUCTION
Play Sea World Puzzle on your Google Chrome Browser with our simple & lightweight extension - No Internet required, no ADS, and 100% Free!

HOW TO INSTALL?
1. Click "Add to Chrome" to install the extension
2. Pin the Sea World Puzzle extension icon to the Chrome toolbar
3. Click the Sea World Puzzle icon on the Chrome toolbar, the Sea World Puzzle popup will open.

That's all you need to do! Have fun!

Play more games on the left-bar menu

HOW TO PLAY?
Match atleast 3 fishes to get them
